File: The power utility is implementing stage 3 load-shedding until 11 o'clock this Friday evening. JPOHANNESBURG - Eskom has downgraded load-shedding to Stage 3 until 11 o'clock this Friday evening. On Saturday, Stage 2 load-shedding will begin at 7am. LOAD-SHEDDING: Schedules, info, and how it affects you The power utility has warned that changes to the load-shedding stages may apply at short notice. Stage 4 was implemented earlier this week after a unit at Koeberg station tripped. South Africans are urged to continue using electricity sparingly.